\v 11 GALA, nii eŐĀ Yesu wuze…†eni, eŐĀ kula saai ya, ni naa naŐĀ-Z…õnvui …†a zeini wo-yiima č…õ, naazu z…Ēi eŐĀ Yesu Kilista wuze…†eni, eŐĀ kula saai ya, naa …†a z…õnvui ve …ďalaa wo-…ďus…õiti zea, ti ga saa gelei, naŐĀ-Z…õnvui zaalai zu, nii eŐĀ zeini wo-yiima č…õ. 
