\q1 eŐĀ k…õ eteai zu, e…†…õ čelei naŐĀ-devei la.¬Ľ\f + \fr 9:27-28 \ft \xt Eza 10:22-23\ft  bog…õ eŐĀ zoloo G…õl…õke woo z…õ č…õ w…Ēl…Ēmai ma.\f* 
